Class Ingredients

  • java.lang.Object
    • menu.Ingredients

  • public class Ingredients
extends java.lang.Object
    This public class creates an objects of ingredients with the data that we have specified here. Than it creates an ArrayList "ingredientsList", with objects Ingredient, and adds ingredients objects to this List.
